<!-- ================= SEMANTIC OVERVIEW (SEO BOOSTER) ================= -->
<section class="section section--lighter section--semantic">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <p>
      VAIRA Technology is a Swiss deep‑tech consultancy specializing in engineering, industrialization, 
      and the development of reliable, scalable technologies. We help organizations move from early 
      concept to industrial performance by combining technical depth with architectural clarity - 
      ensuring solutions that are intentional, robust, and ready for real‑world operation in industrial environments.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= INTRODUCTION ================= -->
<section class="section section--lighter">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <h2>Practical Technology Expertise</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Innovation creates potential.</strong><br>
      <strong>Industrialization turns it into value.</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      VAIRA works at the intersection of technology, engineering, and manufacturing. We help organizations bridge the gap between technical feasibility and scalable, industrial reality.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Our focus is practical: technologies that work, processes that scale, and decisions grounded in engineering understanding.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

